

Encapsulation:-->
		
			=> wrapping up of data into single unit.
			=> Encapsulation helps to prevent accessing data from outside class
			=> Ecapsulation hide data from outside class
			=> it is the mechanism that can access private data outside a class 
						by wrapping data with testcode..
						
						
Advantages:-->
			1. Data Hidding
			2. Flexibility
			3. Reusability
			